title: Standup Comedy - Billy Crystal - Mahvelous! 1985
description:
Transcribed from audio tape, 192 kbps. Features several of his SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE skits.

Mahvelous! - Billy Crystal

Review by Steve Huey 
Mahvelous is a budget-line sampler of Billy Crystals Saturday Night Live routines, which helped make him a star in the early to mid-80s. Although its better to experience the material with the visuals, it is kind of handy to have a lot of it all in one place.
